            { 300, new TwewyPin(300,  "badge_301", "Pig", "ピグ", "Cerdo", "Maiale", "Schwein", "Cochon", "豬", "猪", "[#FF0000]Greatly increases your drop rate[#000000], but in exchange you stop receiving EXP and PP.", "[#FF0000]ドロップレートが大幅にアップ[#000000]する代わりに\nＥＸＰとＢＰがゲットできなくなる", "[#FF0000]Aumenta considerablemente tu tasa de botín[#000000], pero a cambio dejas de recibir EXP y PP.", "[#FF0000]Aumenta notevolmente il tuo tasso di ritrovamenti[#000000], ma in cambio smetti di ricevere ESP e PS.", "[#FF0000]Erhöht deutlich deine Fundrate[#000000], aber dafür erhältst du weder EP noch PP.", "[#FF0000]Augmente considérablement votre taux de butin[#000000] mais, en contrepartie, vous ne recevrez plus d'XP et de PB.", "[#FF0000]掉落率大幅提升[#000000]，\n但卻無法獲得ＥＸＰ與ＰＰ。", "[#FF0000]掉落率大幅提升[#000000]，\n但却无法获得EXP与PP。") },
